##Geʽez Named Entity Recognition (NER)

##Project Done by: Haben Eyasu

This project is done as part of my final project coursework for my NLP course. It focuses on 
Low-Resource language GEEZ (Ancient language from the earliest civilization)NER with Weak Supervision and XLM-R.

The data used follows key value format where the key is english sentence and the value is a parallel geez translation.
 " {
    "gez": "ሔዋን ወቃየን ሖሩ እንተ ባቢሎን እምቅድመ ይፃኡ እምሰማርያ።",
     "eng": "Eve and Cain walked through Babylon before they came up from Samaria."
  }
"

## The project is structured as follows: For simplicity i have compiled all the code in one notebook (ALL-IN-ONE.ipynb) which includes data preprocessing, model training and evaluation.
and tried some test cases.

